.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
There are 2 different favourite colors: brown, purple
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, tram
1. the doctor is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Color         | brown          | purple     |
| Transport   | roller        | tram     |

 